-I have been a passionate
advocate of organic farming

00:24:13.771 --> 00:24:15.238
for 30 years.

00:24:15.238 --> 00:24:17.194
I can still remember
the exact moment

00:24:17.194 --> 00:24:21.106
when I knew I didn't want any
chemicals to grow our food.

00:24:21.106 --> 00:24:24.040
It was just two days
after my husband Drew

00:24:24.040 --> 00:24:27.952
and I moved onto our original
two and 1/2 acre raspberry farm

00:24:27.952 --> 00:24:29.715
in Carmel Valley,
and I was standing

00:24:29.715 --> 00:24:34.022
between two rows of raspberries
near a little orchard of fig

00:24:34.022 --> 00:24:36.557
trees surrounded by the
gorgeous green mountains,

00:24:36.557 --> 00:24:38.992
